description: Spectacular industrial loft situated in the highly sought after Foundry Building. South Boston's hottest neighborhood allows seamless access to the South End, Seaport, Broadway T, top restaurants & bars and all major highways. This brick & beam 1 bed 1 bath condominium offers a galley kitchen, custom cabinets, tiled bath, concrete floors, central heat/ac, storage, huge windows, tastefully finished common areas and 1 gated parking spot.  This property is a great home or investment.
